# AI tool configs (instance-local)
.claude/*
# NOTE (trip hazard): .github/* is an unconditional ignore. Any future tracked GitHub
# config scoped to the backend subtree (e.g. backend/.github/dependabot.yml, a scoped
# CODEOWNERS, project-specific Actions config) will silently fail to track and never
# appear in `git status`. To track such a file, add a whitelist exception below it
# (e.g. `!.github/dependabot.yml`). The pattern itself is intentional — leave it as-is.
.github/*
